{"tid":1983340,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈建議美國 >立即< 暫停香港關系法!!!!","createTime":"2020-04-21T18:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T05:48:50.000Z","uid":252069,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"35704984cae3046883e18e149da9b3ab53f008a6","tid":1983340,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T18:27:39.000Z","msg":"共產黨今日嘅政變其實就係發脾氣<br />\n以為全世界被武漢肺炎折磨緊無力反抗<br />\n又諗著可以呃到全世界自己已抗疫成功<br />\n不停周圍搞戰狼外交<br />\n唔係撩事鬥非咁簡單<br />\n係比個下馬威人捉著人哋隻手教人做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知人哋即刻還拖搞到自己一身傷<br />\n英美澳加紐日德意法台越非 全部都觸礁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(唉真係最叻係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span><br />\n計落喺中國有最多工業嘅國家已經9成(英美加日德)決定走<br />\n即係雜種呢三個月每一步全部都回力標sa<br />\n依家係惱羞成怒喺人哋地頭搞唔到事就喺自己嘅殖民地出手<br />\n好似日本仔要搞釣魚台開發咁擺明就係同你講:&quot;我係要搞, 夠薑你來打我笨柒?!&quot;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(或者南海係好d嘅比喻不過南海主權爭議太分散, 亦唔似日本當年係為啖氣多過為戰略部署)</span><br />\n呢個就係共產黨爛仔邏輯: 諗著比個下馬威你, 等你驚咗我<br />\n但係好易破解: 即刻show quali <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">比返個下馬威轉頭</span></span><br />\n要佢痛、要佢恐嚇、要佢見到你都要掉頭走<br />\n具體做法係:<br />\n強烈建議<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國立即用行政命令暫停香港關系法</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d1aa4058b754f978f8104c399a58316cdcbc20","tid":1983340,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T18:29:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\"